-- Russia c.bank says shifts rouble's trading band by 40 kopecks
-- 
-- Fri Oct 24, 2014 02:12AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, Oct 24 (Reuters) - Russia's central bank said on Friday it had shifted the rouble's trading band by 40 kopecks a day earlier, the largest daily shift in the rouble's trading band so far this year, following market interventions to curb the pace of currency's decline.

